{"title":"各种源配置","date":"2019-09-09T13:51:07.000Z","thumbnail":"/post/各种源配置/cover.jpg","link":"post/各种源配置","tags":["源配置"],"categories":["Misc"],"updated":"2019-09-09T16:19:09.618Z","content":"<h1 id=\"CentOS源\">CentOS源<a href=\"post/各种源配置#CentOS源\"></a></h1><p><strong>备份repo文件</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /etc/yum.repos.d/</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo mkdir bak</span><br><span class=\"line\">mv ./*.repo ./bak/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p><strong>下载repo文件</strong><br>阿里源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>网易源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://mirrors.163.com/.<span class=\"built_in\">help</span>/CentOS7-Base-163.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p><strong>重建yum缓存</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo yum clean all</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo yum makecache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"Pip源\">Pip源<a href=\"post/各种源配置#Pip源\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"VirtualBox下CentOS克隆","link":"post/VirtualBox下CentOS克隆"},"next":{"title":"CentOS网络配置","link":"post/CentOS网络配置"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/各种源配置/","toc":[{"title":"CentOS源","id":"CentOS源","index":"1"},{"title":"Pip源","id":"Pip源","index":"2"}]}